imdb.plot outline: Two brothers, Jake and Matt Green, travel the world on a shoestring budget in order to teach you how to do the same. They've traveled to over 35 countries and counting, learning everything they can about the places they visit and the people they meet. They truly believe that travel broadens the mind and enhances your life, so they want to demonstrate that anyone can explore the world, even those with a less-than-ideal bank account. So join them on an adventure and discover the beautiful places and wonderful people that inhabit this world.
imdb.title: Back to the Peaceful Sea
akas: Back to the Peaceful Sea (United States)
plot: This is the account of two brothers as they trek across the globe and the beautiful things they find along the way.

Two brothers, Jake and Matt Green, travel the world on a shoestring budget in order to teach you how to do the same. They've traveled to over 35 countries and counting, learning everything they can about the places they visit and the people they meet. They truly believe that travel broadens the mind and enhances your life, so they want to demonstrate that anyone can explore the world, even those with a less-than-ideal bank account. So join them on an adventure and discover the beautiful places and wonderful people that inhabit this world.
